---
// Static editorial content for OANDA Prop Trader
// Supports multiple sections via the `section` prop
interface Props {
  section: string;
  fallbackBody?: string;
}
const { section, fallbackBody } = Astro.props;
---

{/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{/* CHALLENGES SECTION                                                  */}
{/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{section === "challenges" && (
<div class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">

  <!-- Overview -->
  <p class="mb-4">
    OANDA Prop Trader now offers a single two step challenge across all account sizes, after fully retiring the old Boost model. The structure is consistent from $5K up to $500K, with the main differences appearing at the top-end account in how drawdown and consistency rules are applied.
  </p>

  <!-- Challenge summary cards -->
  <div class="space-y-3 mb-8">
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Two Step Challenge — $5K to $200K</p>
      <p>Account sizes from $5,000 to $200,000 with fees starting at $35. Phase 1 and Phase 2 both require a 5% profit target. Static drawdown with a fixed 5% daily loss limit based on initial balance.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-teal-600 font-semibold mt-1">Merging allowed up to $200K combined allocation</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Two Step Challenge — $500K</p>
      <p>The premium $500K account at $2,400. Phase 1 requires an 8% profit target, Phase 2 requires 5%. Uses trailing drawdown and dynamic daily loss based on previous end-of-day equity.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-amber-600 font-semibold mt-1">Trailing drawdown and stricter daily profit cap of 5%</p>
